struts里上传图片jpg格式时遇到的问题：<!--more-->
<div>
<h2>struts2 jpg文件上传失败 Content-Type not allowed</h2>
</div>
<div id="content">

org.apache.struts2.interceptor.FileUploadInterceptor - Content-Type not allowed: upload "upload__75549ca5_1239ddc5ce6__8000_00000161.tmp" image/jpg

struts.xml里的原有配置：

&lt;action name="xxxAction"
&gt;
&lt;interceptor-ref name="fileUpload"&gt;
&lt;param name="allowedTypes"&gt;
<span style="color: #ff0000;"> image/bmp,image/png,image/gif,image/jpeg,image/jpg</span>
&lt;/param&gt;
&lt;param name="maximumSize"&gt;200000000000&lt;/param&gt;
&lt;/interceptor-ref&gt;
&lt;interceptor-ref name="defaultStack" /&gt;
&lt;result&gt;/welcome.jsp&lt;/result&gt;
&lt;/action&gt;

<span style="text-decoration: underline;">原因：ie会把 jpg、jpeg翻译成image/pjpeg，png翻译成image/x-png 。而火狐则很标准：jpg、jpeg翻译成image/jpeg，png翻译成image/png。</span>

解决方法：

&lt;param name="allowedTypes"&gt;
<span style="color: #ff0000;"> image/bmp,image/png,image/gif,image/jpeg,image/jpg,image/x-png, image/pjpeg</span>
&lt;/param&gt;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

</div>
